reviewText: This is not a season but rather a few chosen episodes

Love this old clean classic comedy that takes me back to my child hood days. My only regret is that they include Winston cigarette commercials from back in that day. Which I think have the potential to influence impressionable young kids. If it weren't for that I would have definately given this 5 stars.
arrived on time.  product exactly as described.  very satisfied.
They don't show sitcoms on TV anymore, like they did in the golden days! I love watching the hillbillies....especially Granny!
